1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,000
Ahhh...we learned a lot from those years, Kuku

2
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:10,000
We thought we had it all figured out...

3
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:15,024
Until we ran out of oil!

4
00:00:15,024 --> 00:00:21,015
We almost lost everything we built!

5
00:00:21,015 --> 00:00:26,027
Those difficult times brought out the best of us...we knew tourism was the answer for Abu Lumba.

6
00:00:26,027 --> 00:00:33,010
We used the little money we had to build fabulous skyscrapers, hotels, and malls.

7
00:00:33,010 --> 00:00:38,010
But starting Lumba Airlines was our shining moment. Our planes flew in tourists from all over the world and put our city on the map!

8
00:00:38,010 --> 00:00:43,022
I am really proud of what we did, Kuku.

9
00:00:43,022 --> 00:00:49,014
Oh, we arrived? Please hand me my bisht.

10
00:00:29,014 --> 00:01:00,015
Like I always said, Kuku, hard work and good luck can only breed success.

11
00:01:00,015 --> 00:01:07,020
Onwards and upwards!
